<div class="l-rise-tool c-rise-tool">
  {{#if wallConfig}}
    <div class="l-duraark-tool__pane-two">
      {{#if selectedRoom}}
        <div class="c-rise-tool__header">
          <button class="c-rise-tool__back" {{action "backToFloorplan"}}><i class="fa fa-arrow-left"></i>&nbsp; Back</button>
          <header class="c-rise-tool__label">Showing: <strong>{{selectedRoom.label}}</strong>
          </header>

          <h3>Double click a room on the left to add it to the 3D preview. Double click inside the 3D preview to set the center of rotation.</h3>

        </div>
        <hr>

        <div class="l-image-presenter">
          {{#if roomX3DUrl}}
            <h2 class="l-image-presenter__header"><i style="margin-right: 0.4em;" class="fa fa-eye"></i> 3D Preview</h2>
            {{x3d-viewer url=roomX3DUrl}}
          {{else}}
            <h2 class="l-image-presenter__header"><i style="margin-right: 0.4em;" class="fa fa-eye"></i> 3D Preview loading ...</h2>
            {{inline-spinner}}
          {{/if}}
        </div>

        <div class="l-image-presenter">
          <div class="l-image-presenter__header"><i style="margin-right: 0.4em;" class="fa fa-image"></i> Hypothesis Results</div>

          <div class="l-image-list">
            {{#each selectedRoom.hypothesis.walls as |img|}}
              <div class="l-image">
                <img {{action "clickImage" img}} src="{{img}}" alt="Hypothesis Result Image" />
              </div>
            {{/each}}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="l-image-presenter">
          <div class="l-image-presenter__header"><i style="margin-right: 0.4em;" class="fa fa-image"></i> Installation Zones</div>

          <div class="l-image-list">
            {{#each selectedRoom.grammar.walls as |img|}}
              <div class="l-image">
                <img {{action "clickImage" img}} src="{{img}}" alt="Rule Set Image" />
              </div>
            {{/each}}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="l-image-presenter">
          <h2 class="l-image-presenter__header"><i style="margin-right: 0.4em;" class="fa fa-image"></i> Detection Results</h2>

          <div class="l-image-list">
            {{#each selectedRoom.orthophoto.walls as |img|}}
              <div class="l-image">
                <img {{action "clickImage" img}} src="{{img}}" alt="Detection Result Image" />
              </div>
            {{/each}}
          </div>
        </div>

      {{else}}
        <!-- selectedRoom -->
        <h1>Select a room on the floor plan!</h1>
      {{/if}}
    </div>

    <div class="l-duraark-tool__pane-one">
      {{duraark-floorplan wallConfig=wallConfig roomClicked="roomClicked"}}
    </div>
  {{else}}
    This tool generates a hypothesis of the in-wall electrical appliance configuration from a pointcloud scan. The generation is currently in progress, be patient.

    <br>
    <br> After the generation is finished the results will be displayed here. The images below show the result of the electrical appliance detection in three groups. For each detected wall the hypothesis of the electrical appliance is shown, together with
    the rule set applied to the algorithm. As third group the detection of electrical sockets, e.g. power switches, is shown.
  {{/if}}
</div>
